    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Culinarium</i> 是一款卡牌管理类的烹饪游戏，你可以通过将食材和员工堆叠在不同的厨房工具上来做菜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以把它想象成 <i>Stacklands</i> 与 <i>Overcooked</i> 的结合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/be2a53096cb599352f5a99f30f0ecd88.poster.avif?t=1742721561\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/be2a53096cb599352f5a99f30f0ecd88.webm?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/be2a53096cb599352f5a99f30f0ecd88.mp4?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/f3bad557d4468caa9ae9db5130c5264e.poster.avif?t=1742721561\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/f3bad557d4468caa9ae9db5130c5264e.webm?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/f3bad557d4468caa9ae9db5130c5264e.mp4?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会打开补充包获得卡牌，然后可以堆叠这些卡牌来制作各种菜肴，并出售它们。赚取的钱可以用来购买更多的补充包，解锁新的食材、厨房工具和食谱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/fff6d8688c1f26fd80cb4fafe37474ba.poster.avif?t=1742721561\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/fff6d8688c1f26fd80cb4fafe37474ba.webm?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/fff6d8688c1f26fd80cb4fafe37474ba.mp4?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还需要应对偶尔出现的随机事件，比如老鼠试图偷吃你的食材，火灾，或苛刻的美食评论家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/0ccc4f6f2bbe17ca0118568d475ec8e0.poster.avif?t=1742721561\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/0ccc4f6f2bbe17ca0118568d475ec8e0.webm?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/0ccc4f6f2bbe17ca0118568d475ec8e0.mp4?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有两种模式：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险模式：你将通过4个章节（意大利、美国、日本和法国）一步步成为顶级厨师。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/c18d019332ad616d775568656973ec78.poster.avif?t=1742721561\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/c18d019332ad616d775568656973ec78.webm?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/c18d019332ad616d775568656973ec78.mp4?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由模式：你可以随心所欲地烹饪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/31ad08dfe484b0cba09ec05bfa25940d.poster.avif?t=1742721561\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/31ad08dfe484b0cba09ec05bfa25940d.webm?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/31ad08dfe484b0cba09ec05bfa25940d.mp4?t=1742721561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
